    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/7d6071703d2da64b74b2fcd281a817f1.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=158 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Agent Fall 是一款受经典游戏启发的动作游戏，你将面对一个星际政府阴谋。外星人站在政府一边，作为特工的你必须击败这个黑暗联盟。准备好迎接疯狂的战斗，强大的武器、无情的敌人和史诗般的boss等着你。你是否有足够的勇气揭露真相，拯救人类？ </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>单人或与朋友一起玩！（本地合作模式）</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/8677594603b90fcf0526ba3fa4403da8.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无情的敌人和boss！ </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/31b92623dc99724db8e10362409ea597.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的环境和可玩角色。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/efe60a75248a9c3285b785a338ef2b9b.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>尊敬的武器库！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.poster.avif?t=1769279112\" width=622 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.webm?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220110/extras/146cd44e2c3fc412a86a7d5b969e4e17.mp4?t=1769279112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
